      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CHRONIC CHARLIE (1) has finished in the placings both career runs so far, the latest when third (23.64) at this track. Good beginner and aided by the inside draw. Rates strongly and expected to feature again. ZIPPING EMILY (5) was below best at her last couple, the latest finishing fifth at Maitland, but was among the placings at Maitland three back. Solid beginner and with a good start can clear the tricky draw. Can hit the frame this time. FLYING ZAC (2) has an honest record despite remaining a maiden and overdue for a win, having placed seven of 16 career runs. Safe beginner who has drawn to advantage. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. ZIPPING AMOS (3) is a last-start placegetter in a fast-run race - should be thereabouts.",
